{"tid":1165623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"富豪開飛機啟動自駕性侵她　少女嘗禁果欲罷不能","createTime":"2019-05-22T02:03:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T02:43:48.000Z","uid":72009,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9c35100a7205da443edf37efa7c21bea92fb3db1","tid":1165623,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T02:03:34.000Z","msg":"美國紐澤西一名53歲富豪梅爾(Stephen Mell)，以教導開飛機為名義，引誘一名15歲少女，更在開飛機的過程中啟動自駕模式，趁機性侵少女，但沒想到少女嘗禁果後卻欲罷不能，繼續維持與梅爾的不倫戀。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，這名少女在媽媽的推薦下，讓梅爾成為她的開飛機導師，進行一對一教學。兩人的「是姦情」就在2017年的暑假發生，當時梅爾先和少女透過簡訊進行連絡作業，但梅爾除了傳授行前知識，還和少女討論不少性知識，包括如何做愛、如何節育等等，梅爾更在7月6日買了緊急避孕藥。一周後，兩人在紐澤西索莫賽特機場(Somerset Airport)碰面，梅爾也執行對少女進行開飛機的教學。<br />\n<br />\n梅爾的飛機教學路線，從紐澤西飛到鱈魚角(Cape Cod)，但就在回程的途中，梅爾直接啟動了自駕模式，並在飛機上當場性侵少女。不過少女嘗禁果後欲罷不能，沒有反抗梅爾，兩人持續不倫戀直到11月。<br />\n<br />\n該案在去年爆發開來，檢察官也查到梅爾與少女之間有多封情色簡訊，包括梅爾告訴少女：「如果你緊張就會痛痛，如果好好接受就會很OK。」不過梅爾供稱，自己帶少女到他的百萬豪宅，兩人只有進行口交。<br />\n<br />\n梅爾最後被控危險駕駛飛機、非法與未成年者發生性關係等罪，並被沒收飛機駕照，他在以100萬美元(約新台幣3000萬元)交保後，妻子與他離婚並帶走3個孩子。該案將在今日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190522/640_a750c604bea6e6e48ff0e786c97076f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190522%2F640_a750c604bea6e6e48ff0e786c97076f5.jpg&h=e1b43320&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190522/1570938/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190522%2F1570938%2F&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=5fff300d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190522%2F1570938%2F&h=da73cffe\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190522/1570938/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有錢...有幼幼老母幫拖 , 食完幼幼變SP"},{"pid":"09a6a59e88566adfb03422e3c6870090d3ca94fa","tid":1165623,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T02:05:11.000Z","msg":"很想要吧"},{"pid":"3c892ade0ca70484aff00caaea4f28c6bf769ebc","tid":1165623,"uid":60814,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T02:05:26.000Z","msg":"你情我願都性侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64af637805ecc7da711ea278b02a6ca0b0d370a8","tid":1165623,"uid":55386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T02:06:19.000Z","msg":"富豪 有飛機 邊有得輸"},{"pid":"48a2d696fae2f416d7b5dcfe39d641d6f9837c39","tid":1165623,"uid":19126,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T02:07:14.000Z","msg":"成件事有咩問題，感覺連女方個老母都好樂意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f6ba90f7e633a6b3a2bb1615c222a3138c8d9b","tid":1165623,"uid":33477,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T02:08:13.000Z","msg":"十五歲已經學揸飛機<br />\n我廿幾歲都未考車牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3359d74b70ee76a0d8411e5fdf3ef93293de98f3","tid":1165623,"uid":33477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48a2d696fae2f416d7b5dcfe39d641d6f9837c39","tid":1165623,"uid":19126,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T02:07:14.000Z","msg":"成件事有咩問題，感覺連女方個老母都好樂意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T02:09:47.000Z","msg":"飛機開左自動駕駛<br />\n飛機師都要monitor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bbb5def71f32cfd47a634181fb87e19ff233e4c","tid":1165623,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T02:10:26.000Z","msg":"有$$掂吓手都潮吹啦<